&lt;h1 id="why-you-cant-hire"&gt;Why You Can&amp;rsquo;t Hire&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dec 13 2011&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There isn&amp;rsquo;t a shortage of developers and designers. There&amp;rsquo;s a surplus of founders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The cost of starting a company has collapsed. It&amp;rsquo;s now just (minimal) salaries. For entrepreneurs, desks are free, hosting is free, marketing is online, and company setup is cheap.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>